File-Based Log Analyzer (C++17)
Real-world console project

Build:
    g++ -std=gnu++17 main.cpp -o log_analyzer
Run:
    ./log_analyzer ../data/app.log ../reports/summary.txt


Sample data/app.log
-------------------
2025-01-25 10:01:02 INFO User login success user=shiv
2025-01-25 10:02:10 ERROR Database connection failed
2025-01-25 10:03:45 WARN Disk usage high
2025-01-25 10:04:01 INFO User logout user=shiv

